snippet.title: Assassin's Creed Americas Collection: AC3, AC4, Liberation & Release Date! On PC, Xbox 360, PS3
snippet.description:
NEW! Assassin's Creed Americas Collection (aka Birth of a New World in UK) coming to PS3, Xbox 360, PC & release date info. What about PS4, Xbox One?  Would you like to see a version dedicated to the new-gen consoles?
